Dialogs.Dialog: I just had a haircut... Don't you have anything to say？
Hey, my hair is shorter now. What do you think？
I tried this semi-long hairstyle... Don't you have anything to say？
Hey, hey. What do you think about this hairstyle？
Rinko's hair is much longer now, right？
My hair is longer now. What's your opinion？
Hey, my hair is longer now. Do I look feminine？
Okay, you like this then. I see.
Really？ Hehe. Well, if you said that you didn't like it, I would kick you！
Hehehe. That's good. Now, Rinko's charm level is going up, right？
Eh！？ This is very difficult. Hah...
No way. I thought you would like it...
I see. I won't do this style anymore.
Here's the new hairstyle. Now, evaluation time.
Here, how is it？ My new hairstyle.
Say... I changed my hairstyle. How is it？ Weird？
I got it. I'll keep it like this for a while.
Hmm？ Really？ So you like it like this.
I wanted to try some changes, so...
Do you like my new image？ Hey, tell me what you think.
ねえねえ。リンコ、イメチェンしてみたんだけど。
▲小早川＊▲！？ You changed your hair color...
Just wanted to change the mood a bit...
▲小早川＊▲！！ You changed your hair color...
Hey, tell me what you think.
▲小早川＊▲！！ You changed your hair color...
Hey, hey. How's Rinko's image change？
Just wanted to change the mood a bit...
Rinko's image has changed somehow, right？
Hey, hey. Rinko tried this image change.
I tried to look more mature. Does this look suit me？
I'm wearing this mature looking outfit. What do you think？
What do you think about this neat, lady-like look for Rinko？
I tried this cute outfit. Does it suit me？
Do you like my new image？ Hey, tell me what you think.
I tried to look cute. What do you think？
Do you like this style of clothing？
Hey, look. I tried this casual outfit. How do I look？
Occasionally, it's good to wear something like this, huh...？
I tried this style of clothing... Hey, do you have anything to say？
If you like it, it's fine
What do you think？ I tried this sexy outfit this time.
I see. Then I'll keep this look for a while.
Okay, okay. I'll keep wearing this style of clothing from now on.
Hehe. I'm glad. Then I'll keep wearing this style from now on.
I see... Then I'll stop wearing this...
I chose this because I thought you would like it....This is a shock.
What？ If you don't say what you think clearly, how can I know？
...I really tried my best for this. This isn't worth my effort at all.
...Ah, I see. You don't care then.
Are you ignoring me...？ Fine, then！
What do you think about my outfit today？
(Hmm？ It's the same as what she usually wears, isn't it？)
What do you think about my outfit today？
(Hmm？ This is similar to what she usually wears...)
Hey, do you like this neat-and-tidy clothing style？
Do you think this outfit suits Rinko？
I tried this outfit today. ...What do you think？
(This is the cute style that she usually wears.)
What do you think about my fashion today？
What do you think about this outfit？
Hey, hey. Do I look different today？
Hehe, right？ I already thought you'd say that.
I see. You didn't like it. I thought you would, though.
Eh？ I chose this because I thought you would like it.
I see. Then I'll try harder next time.
That's it？ Well, that's fine, though.
What's with that answer？ Can't you just honestly say that you like it？
That's not what I asked you！ Ah, this is enough！
